3代幻之岛计算器 v1.3
GEN3 Mirage island calculator v1.3

　　• 图文攻略地址: 百度贴吧
　　• 视频攻略地址:
　　• 单独演示视频地址: B站， 油管
　　• Walkthrough(word) address: BaiduTieba
　　• Walkthrough(video) address:
　　• Separate operation record(video) address: Bilibili， Youtube

　　• 需要下载的工具: rtcread（按需点击gba、 nds以获得不同客户端的对应软件， 软件源代码点此。）
　　• Tool you need to download: rtcread (Click gba or nds to get different paltform of rtcread you need. Source code click here)

第1步：确保处在非RTC漏洞状态
Stpe 1: Make sure you’re not in RTC glitch

　　• 通过时间相关事件,如种树果,抽奖等,触发事件后保存,rtcread修改时间至后1天,对比能否再次触发,来判断是否处于RTC漏洞状态.
　　• Through time-based event such as berry, lottery. After lanuching event and saving, use rtcread to change rtc to next day. Then check whether you can lanuch event again or not to judge if you are in glitch.

第2步：推算初始RTC
Stpe 2: Get your Initial-RTC

　　• 前往暮水镇西南角房屋，与宝可梦发烧友俱乐部会长的弟弟对话。具体流程详见攻略说明。
　　• Go to Southwest of Pacifidlog Town, talk with Pokemon fan's club chairman's younger brother. For more infomation, please see my walkthrough.

第3步：获取晃晃斑PID
Stpe 1: Get Spinda's PID

　　• 请点击[这里]以查询你晃晃斑的PID。
　　• Please click here to check your Spindas' PID.

第4步：搜索匹配PID的经过RTC天数
Step 4: Search Elapsed-RTC-Days matching Spinda's PID

　　• 请输入第3步中获得的晃晃斑PID后四位（十六进制）：
　　• Please enter the last four digits of the PID (hex) you get in Step 3:

范围（range）：0000~FFFF

第5步：确定出现幻之岛的目标RTC
Step 3: Get the Target-RTC when Mirage island appers

　　• 请输入经过RTC天数和初始RTC。
　　• Please enter the Elapsed-RTC-Days and the Initial-RTC.

　　【注1】：目标RTC接近2099年的，不建议采用，易触发2099漏洞。
　　【注2】：由于仅计算日月年，不考虑时分秒，所得到的目标RTC可能会有前后1天左右的误差，重新调整RTC即可。
　　【注3】：若发现实际RTC无法触发，切勿存档！！！切勿存档！！！切勿存档！！！直接关机再用时钟修复软件调整RTC。
　　【注4】：目标RTC必须大于你保存时的对应RTC，否则无法触发幻之岛，而是进入漏洞状态。
　　【Warning1】：Target-RTC near 2099 years aren't recommended to choose cause 2099 glitch may happen easily.
　　【Warning2】：Your Target-RTC calculated may have 1 day before or after the real Target-RTC which can lanuch your Mirage island, cause we just calculate day，month and year without calculating hour, minute and second. Just change your RTC again.
　　【Warning3】：When you find your RTC cannot lanuch your Mirage island, NEVER! NEVER! NEVER! save your game. Just turn off your gba and use rtcread to change your rtc.
　　【Warning4】：Target-RTC must later than the RTC when you save game, or you game will be in glitch and won't lanuch Mirage island.
